{"tid":1336011,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"係大圍連儂天橋貼手畫長輩圖果位巴/C打，請入一入黎","createTime":"2019-07-20T18:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T01:01:39.000Z","uid":41366,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"725a6afb100671e76460f6c16091afc85358b6b1","tid":1336011,"uid":41366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:00:25.000Z","msg":"岩岩將你原本貼係包書膠既畫作<br />\n移到去牆上邊（往大圍方向靠近單車徑既天橋）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知你有冇睇連登，但都想同你講返聲<br />\n唔好心掛掛，以為俾人撕走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">希望唔好俾藍屍廢老整爛la</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x1wkQrH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx1wkQrH.png&h=7a268365&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AGTfEj4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAGTfEj4.png&h=032e9ae3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6UPOeTq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6UPOeTq.png&h=6ed3cec3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋多謝今晚咁多位巴C打為連儂天橋<br />\n進行修復工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FR4njn0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFR4njn0.png&h=3aaaaf0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有位絲打整既time line<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6yR5g7X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR5g7X.png&h=3083bc04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖入邊寫咩就自己行去大圍八爪魚天橋到睇la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw<br />\n聽日3點見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f778086ce302c77a67bf0212eea037862c0d6657","tid":1336011,"uid":182575,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:02:39.000Z","msg":"痴線 靚到"},{"pid":"da0344d7f941cdfeb8a9dfe7bc8c9a38cbdc5f65","tid":1336011,"uid":41366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f778086ce302c77a67bf0212eea037862c0d6657","tid":1336011,"uid":182575,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:02:39.000Z","msg":"痴線 靚到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:03:32.000Z","msg":"希望唔好俾班仆街界爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7eb59d6cdbaf6f8fda863fc34ad9b1e876fcd7e","tid":1336011,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:04:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f60f8f29a1e3691bd89ab565cadad63ecba367ba","tid":1336011,"uid":41366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:06:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3fe5c0ba27c6a9ba6f208b71bd028c5f9d63ce1f","tid":1336011,"uid":14244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:07:07.000Z","msg":"好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d6381ba685e69f5a228c31a72b5630d249c7fe0","tid":1336011,"uid":41366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:07:29.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n推到俾佢知，你幅畫暫時完好無缺<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor